  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Step into the shadows of Santa Tereza Mansion.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What should have been a simple reconnaissance mission turns into an unimaginable nightmare. Three forest policemen and an ABIN agent are sent to investigate the mysterious isolated mansion in the mountains of Petrópolis. But something goes terribly wrong — and the team is separated by dark forces that defy logic.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You take on the role of Marcos Nunes, a veteran agent who must now fight alone for survival. Explore every corner of the mansion in search of answers, gather scarce resources, and face grotesque creatures lurking in the dark corridors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Deadly Contagion</strong> brings back the essence of classic survival horror:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A tense and oppressive atmosphere</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenging environmental puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Terrifying encounters full of suspense</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An engaging narrative filled with secrets and revelations</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570740/extras/38cfd8da08e41ea64bb1d60935f20280.poster.avif?t=1769111202\" width=780 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570740/extras/38cfd8da08e41ea64bb1d60935f20280.webm?t=1769111202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570740/extras/38cfd8da08e41ea64bb1d60935f20280.mp4?t=1769111202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">⚠️ <strong>Beware of the infected!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570740/extras/8d07d75ee9d5f56e39c902385319a6f0.poster.avif?t=1769111202\" width=780 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570740/extras/8d07d75ee9d5f56e39c902385319a6f0.webm?t=1769111202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570740/extras/8d07d75ee9d5f56e39c902385319a6f0.mp4?t=1769111202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Manage your inventory</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570740/extras/d725c417ed0c0ac0d9012838eec099ef.poster.avif?t=1769111202\" width=780 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570740/extras/d725c417ed0c0ac0d9012838eec099ef.webm?t=1769111202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570740/extras/d725c417ed0c0ac0d9012838eec099ef.mp4?t=1769111202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Survive!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">⚠️ <strong>Get ready. Not everyone will make it out of Santa Tereza alive.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Step into the shadows of Santa Tereza Mansion.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What should have been a simple reconnaissance mission turns into an unimaginable nightmare. Three forest policemen and an ABIN agent are sent to investigate the mysterious isolated mansion in the mountains of Petrópolis. But something goes terribly wrong — and the team is separated by dark forces that defy logic.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You take on the role of Marcos Nunes, a veteran agent who must now fight alone for survival. Explore every corner of the mansion in search of answers, gather scarce resources, and face grotesque creatures lurking in the dark corridors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Deadly Contagion</strong> brings back the essence of classic survival horror:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A tense and oppressive atmosphere</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenging environmental puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Terrifying encounters full of suspense</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An engaging narrative filled with secrets and revelations</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570740/extras/38cfd8da08e41ea64bb1d60935f20280.poster.avif?t=1769111202\" width=780 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570740/extras/38cfd8da08e41ea64bb1d60935f20280.webm?t=1769111202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570740/extras/38cfd8da08e41ea64bb1d60935f20280.mp4?t=1769111202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">⚠️ <strong>Beware of the infected!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570740/extras/8d07d75ee9d5f56e39c902385319a6f0.poster.avif?t=1769111202\" width=780 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570740/extras/8d07d75ee9d5f56e39c902385319a6f0.webm?t=1769111202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570740/extras/8d07d75ee9d5f56e39c902385319a6f0.mp4?t=1769111202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Manage your inventory</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570740/extras/d725c417ed0c0ac0d9012838eec099ef.poster.avif?t=1769111202\" width=780 height=584 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570740/extras/d725c417ed0c0ac0d9012838eec099ef.webm?t=1769111202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2570740/extras/d725c417ed0c0ac0d9012838eec099ef.mp4?t=1769111202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Survive!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">⚠️ <strong>Get ready. Not everyone will make it out of Santa Tereza alive.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
